# Files to be ignored in the context of Python

## Python-generated files
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[oc]
**/build/
**/dist/
**/wheels/
**/*.egg-info

## Virtual environments
**/.venv/

## Environment files
**/*.env
**/*.env.*

## Testing
**/.coverage

## Linting / Formatting
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.ruff_cache/
